title: RHONY Season 11 Reunion Part 3 Recap + A Word on Camille (#RHOBH)
itunes:title: RHONY Season 11 Reunion Part 3 Recap + A Word on Camille (#RHOBH)
itunes:subtitle: Danny bids adieu to the queens/icons/legends of #RHONY season 11 with a recap of part 3 of the reunion. In the final episode, Barb joins the couch with a questionable tanning choice, Lu confronts vocal critiques, announces a role on Broadway, and more!...
description:
Danny bids adieu to the queens/icons/legends of #RHONY season 11 with a recap of part 3 of the reunion. In the final episode, Barb joins the couch with a questionable tanning choice, Lu confronts vocal critiques, announces a role on Broadway, and more! Plus, a few words on Camille's #RHOBH reunion performance.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
